item.title: CVE-2020-4486|2024-08-04T08:07:48.934Z -- ibm -- qradar%20wincollect
item.description: IBM QRadar 7.2.0 thorugh 7.2.9 could allow an authenticated user to overwrite or delete arbitrary files due to a flaw after WinCollect installation. IBM X-Force ID: 181861.

item.title: CVE-2020-4485|2024-08-04T08:07:48.578Z -- ibm -- qradar%20wincollect
item.description: IBM QRadar 7.2.0 through 7.2.9 could allow an authenticated user to disable the Wincollect service which could aid an attacker in bypassing security mechanisms in future attacks. IBM X-Force ID: 181860.
